      The code is a massively hacked offshoot of the early versions
      of Galaxy plus substantial new code. The home page of Blind Galaxy 
      is on ALink(`http://www.cs.utk.edu/~bampton/blind.html',
      `http://www.cs.utk.edu/~bampton/blind.html'). 
  </LI>

  <LI>Galaxy PBW, a verion of Blind Galaxy that can be played via
      the WWW. The home page is on
      ALink(`http://pc046b.fzu.cz/galaxywww/', 
      `http://pc046b.fzu.cz/galaxywww/').</LI>

  <LI>Galaxy plus (G+). A variation of the game developed in Russia
      somewhat similar to GalaxyNG but there are 
