      `Software Archive'), ALink(`http://galaxy.spb.ru/',
      `News and Links'), ALink(`http://www.lgg.ru/~agator/',
      `More news and links'),
      ALink(`http://www.sargona.ru/pbem/', `Sargona server'),
      ALink(`http://www.games.ru/galaxy/', `First Moscow server'). 
  </LI>

  <LI>ALink(`index2.html', `GalaxyNG').  This is a partial rewrite of
      the original code to create a more stable version of galaxy
      developed by a number of people. It also introduces some changes
      to the rules and the option to create more diverse kinds of
      galaxies.  There are two main servers. One is run by Robert
      Hayden, for a status of his games see
      ALink(`http://galaxy.geek.net', `http://galaxy.geek.net').  The
